para_trans: On extending the term of the committee by appointing invited members to the Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti.
Department of Higher and Technical Education
Government Decision No: Sankarna 2024 / Q. 22/721067 MASHI-2
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,

Reference: - (1) Government Decision, Department of Higher and Technical Education, No.2020 / (Q. 80/20) / Aastha-2D. 1st August, 2020 (2) Government Decision, Department of Higher and Technical Education, No. Committee 2022 / No.72 / Aastha-2, D. July 7, 2023

Introduction: - Reference No. Under Section 1, the Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti was formed and the term of the committee was kept for three years. Reference No. Invited members have been appointed to the committee under section 2. The government was considering extending the term of the committee by appointing new invitees to the committee.

Government Decision: - The following dignitaries, who are biographers of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, have been appointed as invited members on the Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Charitra Sadhana Prakashan Samiti vide Government Decision dated 7th July, 2023.
In addition to the above-mentioned invited members, the following dignitaries who were biographers of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj are being newly appointed as invited members.
The term of the said Committee shall be till 30th June, 2024.
4. Government Decision No. The composition, procedure, terms and conditions and allowances of the Committee as prescribed under section 1B2 shall continue.
5. This Government Decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
